# Netlify headers (ignored by other hosts — safe to keep).
# Assets are un-hashed and deploys are manual drag-and-drop, so no long-lived
# immutable caching: a day of cache + revalidation keeps updates visible.
/*
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
/assets/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=86400
